{
    "version": "2021-02-10T20.29.20",
    "description": "提取和重新打包 pyinstaller 生成的 Windows 可执行文件的工具。支持最新版本的 pyinstaller。仅限 Python 3。不支持加密的 PYZ 存档。",
    "homepage": "https://github.com/pyinstxtractor/pyinstaller-repacker",
    "license": "unknown",
    "suggest": {
        "python": "uv"
    },
    "url": "https://github.com/pyinstxtractor/pyinstaller-repacker/archive/refs/heads/master.zip",
    "hash": "",
    "extract_dir": "pyinstaller-repacker-main",
    "pre_install": [
        "Set-Content \"$dir\\pyinstaller-repacker.bat\" '@pushd %~dp0",
        "@uv run python \"pyinst-repacker.py\" %*",
        "@popd' -Encoding Ascii"
    ],
    "post_install": [
        "uv venv \"$dir\\.venv\"",
        "uv pip install lief lxml --python \"$dir\\.venv\\Scripts\\python.exe\""
    ],
    "bin": "pyinstaller-repacker.bat",
    "checkver": {
        "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/pyinstxtractor/pyinstaller-repacker/commits",
        "regex": "([\\d-]+T)(\\d+):(\\d+):(\\d+)",
        "replace": "$1$2.$3.$4"
    },
    "autoupdate": {
        "url": "https://github.com/pyinstxtractor/pyinstaller-repacker/archive/refs/heads/master.zip"
    },
    "notes": [
        "【工具类型】: Python工具",
        "【主要功能】: 提取和重新打包 pyinstaller 生成的 Windows 可执行文件的工具。支持最新版本的 pyinstaller。仅限 Python 3。不支持加密的 PYZ 存档。",
        "【适用场景】: Python逆向分析、PyInstaller打包修改、安全审计",
        "【技术特点】: 基于Python开发，需Python环境"
    ]
}
